description:
Tumble - Series 1, Episode 2




Show Two

All 10 celebrities will perform whichever discipline they did not perform in Show 1 and once again receive comments and scores from the judges. The scores received by each celebrity in show 1 and show 2 will be compared to establish their Personal Best which will be the higher of the two scores. The Personal Best will then be used as their score for the end of show 2 leaderboard. The two celebrities with the lowest scores on the leaderboard at the end of show 2 are the "bottom two". They must now face 'The Vault'. One celebrity will be eliminated after the vault performance.




Original Air Date: 16-Aug-2014
